JamendoGet2Api
          Java interface to the jamendo.get2 API ("The Free Music API")

Musiclist2Api

USAGE:
Basically, since this service does not require any sort of authorization, just write:

JamendoGet2Api service = new JamendoGet2ApiImpl();

NOTE:
This library is meant to cover most of the api documented on the wiki.
